res in the U.S. and <em>more than 20</em> in Japan. There=E2=80=99s also he=
r Adidas collection, now more than two decades running, which positioned
Stella McCartney as a first mover in high-end activewear <em>and</em> brand=
 collaborations. But that was ages ago. At one point, overall Stella McCart=
